reviewText: MARIA PARIS STARS IN THIS WONDERFUL TASTY FILM NOIR RETRO DELIGHT! THIS FEATURETTE IS WELL-MADE, WITH MARIA PARIS PLAYING A RECENT WIDOW AFTER HER HUSBAND WAS MURDERED. BUT IS SHE WHAT SHE SEEMS? WHAT LURKS BEHIND HER LOVELY DARK EYES? THE PERFECT COMPANION PIECE TO MOVIES LIKE "YESTERDAY WAS A LIE". HIGHLY RECOMMENDED!
